{"@type":"Question","name":"Do all ventral hernias need surgery?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Not all. Very small, asymptomatic hernias may be monitored. But hernias tend to enlarge over time, and elective repair is safer than emergency repair."}},
