<section class="content-section alt" id="surgery-day">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <p class="section-label">The day of your procedure</p>
    <h2>What Happens on Surgery Day</h2>
    <div class="surgery-day-steps">
      <div class="sd-step">
        <div class="sd-time">Arrival</div>
        <div class="sd-desc"><strong>Check in 1&ndash;2 hours before your scheduled time.</strong> IV placed, nursing and anesthesia team meet you, Dr. Kakarla visits to mark the hernia site and answer last questions.</div>
