      <div class="sd-step">
        <div class="sd-time">Closure</div>
        <div class="sd-desc"><strong>Incisions sealed with Dermabond</strong> (medical skin adhesive) &mdash; no stitches or staples to remove. Waterproof, sloughs off naturally in 5&ndash;10 days. Brief shower the same day is fine (no soaking). An <strong>abdominal binder</strong> is placed before you leave.</div>
